name: Good Bye
description: One evening I was waiting for my friend. he is always a late comer, never keeps his time. standing there with all my anger, i just looked up to the sky. i saw a beautiful view of Sun saying goodbye to everyone and preparing to go home. today's duty for him ends and he says goodbye to all. it was a beautiful view. but when i looked down i realised that its not just Sun, but everyone is saying goodbye after a days work and are going home. so i thought that when sun says goodbye, its a goodbye for everyone.
